Our Team
BAKER COUNTY FAIR TEAM
The Baker County Fair Association Board and team are the dedicated individuals who work tirelessly behind the scenes to bring the fair to life each year. Their passion, commitment, and teamwork ensure a fun, safe, and memorable experience for the entire community. From organizing events to managing fair operations, each member plays a vital role in preserving this cherished tradition. Meet the faces behind the fair below!
